      "author": "Quorafind",
      "description": "## What's New\n\n### CMDK Quick Search Modal\n- Double-tap Shift (configurable) to invoke a fast search modal with real-time file preview\n- Progressive heading search using Obsidian's metadataCache (zero I/O, instant results)\n- File name/path fuzzy matching + heading fuzzy matching\n- Batched rendering via `chooser.addSuggestion()` for smooth UI\n\n### Settings\n- **Quick search trigger**: Choose between Double Shift / Ctrl / Alt / Meta, or disable\n- **Double-tap interval**: Adjust timing sensitivity (150ms–600ms)\n\n### Fixes\n- Fix `inputEl` undefined errors caused by timing race conditions\n- Fix extra view creation when `defaultViewType` is set to window\n- Add auto-preview on arrow key navigation in FloatSearchModal\n- Use `setViewState` for reliable file navigation with heading subpath support",
